{"type": "article", "id": 15085, "title": "“under the skin”", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-18T07:26:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000339ALFRuoTaX13I98US.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tBrichetziegler Studio 为法国公司 Moustache 设计了一款特别的灯，在两层聚氨酯材料中间夹有一层竹纸板，手工切割后折叠固定，有点像某种动物。开灯的时候，内部的红铜色会显示出来，与蓝色之间形成强烈的撞击，令人印象深刻。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261424210AIr1J4DeoNSwYp7.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"618\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75550122\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261424226KUPtVu39afZGRqi.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"609\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74449878\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142422KO42Tkt8fjvhyiFr.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}